地图作者: 银月筱瑶.Translation: Map Author: 银月筱瑶, EN Translation: AllenW @ Ozlin server

人类掌握了治愈元素的力量.Translation: Humans have mastered the power of healing elements.

我们需要30秒的时间来部署炸药.Translation: We need 30 seconds to deploy the explosives.

门开了，走了！.Translation: The door is open, let's go!

房子的出口有个木门，炸掉它！.Translation: There's a wooden door at the exit of the house; blow it up!

地面的泥土很松软，快找找下面有什么.Translation: The ground is soft; quickly see what's underneath.

25秒后打开实验室大门.Translation: The laboratory door will open in 25 seconds.

这道门还要15秒才能打开.Translation: This door will take another 15 seconds to open.

有一块石头挡住了去路.Translation: A rock is blocking the way.

想办法开路，快！.Translation: Find a way to clear the path, hurry!

快上飞机！不要发呆了！.translation: Get on the plane! Don't just stand there!

给我30秒启动飞机，我们马上就能离开这个鬼地方了！.translation: Give me 30 seconds to start the plane, and we can leave this hellhole!

最后5秒，飞机要走了！.translation: Last 5 seconds, the plane is leaving!

你完成了第一关.translation: You have completed the first level

冰魔法被一位小可爱学会了.translation: A cute one has learned a Ice magic

僵尸掌握了神秘的力量！xing(刀声).translation: The zombie has mastered mysterious powers! xing (sword sound)

僵尸神力已被拿起.translation: Zombie divine power has been picked up

僵尸毒已被拿起.translation: Zombie poison has been picked up

僵尸加速已被拿起.translation: Zombie acceleration has been picked up

人类掌握了风元素的力量.translation: Humans have mastered the power of wind elements

私人弹药库已被拿起.translation: Private ammunition cache has been picked up

地下的入口有许多石头.translation: The underground entrance has many stones

马上去清理，我们时间不多.translation: Go clear it out quickly, we don't have much time

前面似乎是死路.translation: It seems like a dead end ahead

那就干脆把路炸开，别犹豫了.translation: Then let's just blow the path open, don't hesitate

人类掌握了火元素的力量.translation: Humans have mastered the power of fire elements

铁门挡住了路，解锁眼前的大门！.translation: An iron door blocks the way, unlock the door ahead!

直接炸掉了，走！.translation: Blow it up directly, let's go!

这块地板下有水流的声音，可能有水路，快想办法给这块砖砸开.translation: There’s the sound of water flowing under this floor, there might be a waterway, quickly find a way to break this brick

水路已经被打开了, 快跑.translation: The waterway has been opened, run!

电梯需要45秒的时间来激活，一定要坚持住，我们马上就可以离开了.translation: The elevator needs 45 seconds to activate, hold on, we will leave soon

人类掌握了土元素的力量.translation: Humans have mastered the power of earth elements

60秒后我们将引爆炸弹！boom！.translation: The bomb will be detonated in 60 seconds! boom!

这个方向有一条出路.translation: There’s an exit in this direction

准备爆破，我们上山！.translation: Prepare to blow it up, we’re going up the mountain!

路上的障碍物很多.translation: There are many obstacles on the road

快点清理掉障碍物，前面就是山顶了！冲上去！！.translation: Quickly clear the obstacles, the mountaintop is just ahead! Charge up!!

逃离岛屿的大门就在眼前.translation: The gate to escape the island is right in front of us

坚持住，我们马上就可以离开了！.translation: Hold on, we can leave soon!

传送点将会被移至山谷中部.translation: The teleport point will be moved to the middle of the valley

你逃离了跳刀岛....translation: You have escaped from Jump Knife Island...

ze_laser_island天下第一.translation: ze_laser_island is the best in the world

敢惹我，你就是惹到棉花了(つД`).translation: If you provoke me, you'll be messing with cotton (つД`)

吉祥物弹药库已被拿起.translation: Mascot ammunition cache has been picked up

私人弹药库被V社带走了，现在的弹药只是个吉祥物，他会时不时说几句神志不清的话.translation: The private ammo cache has been taken away by Volvo; now the ammo is just a mascot that occasionally says nonsensical things

僵尸登上了飞机.translation: The zombie has boarded the plane

僵尸上船了，本关失败.translation: The zombie boarded the ship, mission failed
